    "date": "2006-11-28T17:35:40Z",
    "text": "Stock Option Accounting Review Act - Amends the Sarbanes-Oxley Act of 2002 to direct the Financial Accounting Standards Board to: (1) review the accounting treatment of employee stock options; and (2) within one year after the enactment of this Act, adopt an appropriate generally accepted accounting principle for the treatment of such options."
